{"id": "1336240252615917589", "channel_id": "1333633554512351262", "type": 0, "author_id": "1157675500014153860", "author_name": "youluo0436", "author_bot": false, "content": "支持！不然覺得蠻不方便的……\n我要給角色裝命輪還要特地去編隊那裡\n然後如果角色不在編隊中還要特地把他放上去……", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T07:41:42.367000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1333633554512351262", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "感觉这个命轮不会脱下来是负优化", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
