{"id": "1336336786489741404", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "官方有針對這個解釋嗎", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:05:17.836000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336337396266172447", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "我一直以為石化會被頂掉是正常的，因為不管是石化後打到二階段覺醒、莉莉＆尤烏扣到一定血量換意圖、圖魯＆彌利狂氣爆發換意圖都是能夠頂掉石化狀態的", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:07:43.218000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336337580148396144", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "石化只有針對當下的攻擊，並沒針對血量與觸發機制條件進行限制", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:08:27.059000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336337669969678431", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "我都是卡在覺醒階段石化的，沒體驗過這樣的情況，第一次", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:08:48.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336337839788396658", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是有過石化打死第一階段然後進二階頂掉石化很多次", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:09:28.962000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336338007539712084", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "就機制的問題還有先後順序", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:10:08.957000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336338013021802579", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 19, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "但石化是用回合計數的，當回合內被石化代表當回合不能行動，轉階段、意圖都算當回合的行動不是嗎", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:10:10.264000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["943113632433197108"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1336337580148396144", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336340118872785028", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "我懂你的意思，因為我一開始也覺得石化的敘述來說就是該讓他一整個回合都沒辦法動。\n只是長期下來的經歷告訴我，你石化除非要弄超限增傷爆發不然都是要最後再開開，不然一個不小心就轉意圖浪費石化。\n可是遊戲的觸發轉意圖機制該轉的時候就是會轉，你只能去改牌序來規避浪費石化。\n石化也許會造成轉意圖時的BUG(直接跳過機制殺那種)，所以才不考慮把石化完全鎖死，但那不是我該去幫忙解釋的地方。\n我挺想看看會不會回覆。", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:18:32.338000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1336340897784266884", "channel_id": "1336327817247457373", "type": 0, "author_id": "944524613168279553", "author_name": "ena04564", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得怕機制殺被鎖的話直接送一層石化抗性比較快", "timestamp": "2025-02-04T14:21:38.045000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1336327817247457373", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊癲婆卡規則Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
